$EDC_book_info['22878'] = array("Women’s Rights &#038; Marriage Rulings between Christianity and Islam", "E-Da`wah Committee (EDC)", "".$site_link."/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/en-Womens_Rights_Marriage_Rulings_between_Christianity_and_Islam.pdf", "".$site_link."/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/en-Womens_Rights_Marriage_Rulings_between_Christianity_and_Islam.png", "Women’s rights are always used for vilifying Islam and espousing Christianity on the pretext that Christianity is mostly deemed more equitable towards women in terms of marriage rulings. The E-Da`wah Committee is pleased to present this publication to explore women’s rights in terms of marriage rulings between Christianity and Islam.", "".$site_link."/?p=22878&lang=English", "164");
